## Constraints

- Event-driven: `@OnEvent('task.created')` listeners in NotificationGenerator
- Notification persistence: DB + TanStack Query cache
- In-app first, email optional (per preference)
- Email: SES + BullMQ queue (async, retry on failure)
- Template: Handlebars syntax (`{{firstName}}, {{taskUrl}}`)
- Preferences: user-level, per event type × per channel (in-app / email / digest)
- Default preferences seeded: critical notifications on (task assigned, SLA overdue), optional off (digest)
- Mark read: single + all
- Cleanup cron: 90 gün eski notification sil

