## Explicit Don'ts

- SMS notifications (post-MVP)
- Push notifications (requires mobile)
- Bulk notification broadcast (admin announcement — post-MVP)
- Notification grouping/threading (flat list MVP)
- Real-time notification push via WebSocket (polling yeter — project identity MVP scope dışı)
- Slack/Teams integration (post-MVP)

